Usage: get_socv_rc_variation_factor [-help] -view <viewName> {-early  | -late }

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-early               # Get the variation factor for early interconnect delays
                     # (bool, optional)
-late                # Get the variation factor for late interconnect delays
                     # (bool, optional)
-view <viewName>     # Get the SOCV interconnect variation factor for specified
                     # view (string, required)